    for i in range(len(string)):  
        if string[i] in visited and start_index <= visited[string[i]]: 
            start_index = visited[string[i]] + 1
        else: 
            max_length = max(max_length, i - start_index + 1) 

        visited[string[i]] = i 

    return max_length
```

